data.description: Prepare to be amazed by this beautiful custom home! Hurry and see this 4 bed, 4.5 bath residence now for sale! Nestled on a premium corner lot and featuring a stunning facade w/stone accents, manicured desert landscape, 3 car side garage, paver driveway & walkways, and a gated front courtyard! Inside you will find a spacious dining & living area w/polished stone floors, recessed lighting, plantation shutters, and neutral palette throughout. Continue into the elegant family room, boasting tray ceilings, engineered hard wood floors, and an impressive stone fireplace! The gorgeous chef's kitchen is comprised of wood cabinetry w/crown moulding, a walk-in pantry, granite counters, stylish backsplash, high end stainless steel appliances, an island w/a breakfast bar, and a breakfast nook. Don't forget about the cozy den, perfect for an office! Sit back and relax in the primary bedroom, w/its separate outdoor access, 2-way fireplace, walk-in closet, and lavish ensuite w/dual sinks. Every other bedroom also includes a private bath for added comfort! Finally, the wonderful backyard includes a covered patio, extended seating areas, a built-in BBQ, artificial turf, view fence, and a sparkling blue pool! The home of your dreams is here, act now!
